            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">能把花园艺术写成一本专业的学术论文，既有趣又充满了学理分析。这样的研究对我很有启发。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="566632706">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-566632706" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-566632706" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="566632706">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/26834247/">Piper Chen</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2012-08-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">啰嗦的要死，到处透露着不自信还是不要搞哲学</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="462249304">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-462249304" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-462249304" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="462249304">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/carmelita/">Xaos Geneto</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-11-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">非常耐读的一小本哲学书，花园之于景观学，就如同构造之于建筑学。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="393784851">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
